Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.39,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The act of bringing two pairs of lips \Ntogether, which we'd never heard of,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.81,0:00:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was called a kiss, she said.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence connecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day after the klaxosaur attack,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.03,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the startup ritual picked up where it left \Noff, but in much quieter circumstances.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.08,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Papa and the other adults weren't \Naround to witness it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.67,0:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was told the huge FRANXX \NI rode was named Strelizia.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.79,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no recollection of anything \Nthat happened after I got in,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.26,0:00:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I still believe that \Nit all really happened,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that I was able to \Nfly under my own power.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm no longer a nestling.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.89,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I swore never to run away again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are mew from around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hiro?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to wait out here for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for running off \Nfirst thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.51,0:02:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Awkward as it is, you're staying here now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your head high,\Nand make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.82,0:03:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Naomi was all right. \NShe got taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.65,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the one piloting that FRANXX?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to ride it again to make sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Again? That girl isn't part \Nof our squad, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care, as long as I get to pilot.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the rumors about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.26,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,None of her partners could ever ride \Nwith her more than three times.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't make it out alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's true or not,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.27,0:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think you should stay away from her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.15,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can't pilot, \NI'm as good as dead anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.99,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiro. Get inside quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's in our mess hall.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why is she still here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What a strange person.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder if she likes sweets.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's not a person. Not with \Nthose things on her head.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cut it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's our savior, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you think she really has klaxosaur blood?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.36,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Besides, I thought nobody \Nhad single-digit codes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's nothing like the rumors said.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's ruining her good looks \Nwith the way she's eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't believe all her \Ninjuries healed so quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, there!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was a real treat to watch \Nyour skills in action.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I, Zorome the Great, shall graciously \Nride with you if you so desire.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.30,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sure I can do a much \Nbetter job than that wuss.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why don't we try... Eek!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, my Sunday best!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do about this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really nice and sweet.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat together, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I actually manage to pilot back then?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure did.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were {\i1}incredible{\i0},
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,darling.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,D...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Doesn't sound like food.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I really did pilot that FRANXX back then!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, keep it down, kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your caretaker, \Njust like I was in Garden.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.82,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}APE HQ has assigned me to the\N13th Plantation Corps. My name is Nana.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I look forward to your cooperation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes! We got lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.20,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Figures.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to stay here?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}For real?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're awaiting orders from HQ \Non what to do with Zero Two.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But in general, she won't \Nbe working with you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. You're sitting over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.51,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, but this table felt more comfortable.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zero Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ride in your FRANXX again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to be sure of.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't for you to decide.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa and the rest will give you \Nyour orders in due time, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit tight until then, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa will?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give orders to him? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was with that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you running off \Nas you please all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to eat with my darling.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid making contact with the parasites.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too much for them to handle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm gonna suffocate in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.89,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Confirmed appearance of one \NMohorovicic-class klaxosaur at Plantation 13.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strelizia intercepted and neutralized it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuel stockpile down to 54 percent.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Currently anchored in the area.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Requesting kissing with Plantation 26.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Authorized.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Roger.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Kissing will commence in 175 hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.66,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received word that Strelizia \Nhas stayed back at Plantation 13.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Another of that girl's whims? \NDr. Franxx spoils her too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case, if you \Njust look at the numbers,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.17,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to be a rare sample \Nwithout signs of physical aging.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Code 016. That's him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unthinkable.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.14,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With no established cause, mixing with the \Nspecial specimen will taint her blood.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be recalled at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But we saw how she shone in that battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth investigating.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait and see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.15,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you managed \Nto fight that klaxosaur.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember how it felt.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I'm glad you stayed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're the type that comes \Nthrough when it matters most.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you got the jump on me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, dude.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.63,0:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe for a second that \Nyou piloted a FRANXX before we did.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that, you wuss?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why are these so tiny?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So tight!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Connecting feels so weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get used to it soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not at all like how \Nour training units felt.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.36,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like your body being \Nstirred up from the inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Miku!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes! Are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop reminding me of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really that rough for you guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It did feel a bit weird, but I dunno...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda put me at ease,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,like I'd become one with someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish my numbers were as high as yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.89,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Goro must be really compatible.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.28,0:09:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you. You two double-digit \Nelites are made for each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of elite, how about that Hiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.32,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He brings home a girl out of nowhere, \Nand she's already calling him "darling."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe those two will actually \Nmake a good coup—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that all about?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be giving out your overall \Nstrategic instructions.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.14,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But the decisions on the field must be \Nmade by the leader unit, Delphinium.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she get to be leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you're ready, we will now begin the drill.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.11,0:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be your first drill \Nin a real FRANXX, but stay calm,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}focus on your partner's movements, \Nand entrust yourself to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Commence connecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.92,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quit making weird noises!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a natural reaction!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If two partners are even \Nslightly out of sync,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,their para-capacity will fluctuate wildly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key is to trust your partners \Nand accept them wholeheartedly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Keep going.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do it right? I didn't suck?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, you were fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're perfectly matched, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa, quit getting all \Nlovey-dovey over this crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was the first to finish, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Got that, double-digits?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And don't you forget it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's in high spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the point of competing \Namong ourselves?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! Sour grapes, much?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup! Unf!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't be rough!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.81,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The stamen has the initiative \Nwhen it comes to handling,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so consider whether the pistil,\Nwho's connected to the FRANXX, can keep up.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miss High-and-Mighty.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.58,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Line up in formation with Delphinium \Nin the center and advance.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did manage to pilot back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.68,0:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could just ride with\NZero Two in Strelizia again,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.94,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.49,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A startup trial in an actual FRANXX?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm{\i1} this {\i0}close to figuring out \Nthe trick to connecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd it have to be Hiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro? You mean my darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, calling him that again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you for \Ndefeating that klaxosaur.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.27,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to stay away \Nfrom Hiro from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're not part of our squad.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.81,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna up and leave one day,\Ndon't get Hiro's hopes up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you to my darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the leader of this squad.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet. I like your taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be able to fight like that one day?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.51,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight the klaxosaurs like the \NFRANXX Hiro piloted, I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what? Just so you know, \Nthat doesn't count as piloting.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that loser \Ncould pilot a FRANXX.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it did actually move around.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And Papa seems to have taken \Nan interest in Hiro, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that pistil called Zero Two
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.53,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,has the special ability to \Npilot a FRANXX by herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You two saw its four-legged form, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, Hiro was only \Ntaken along for the ride.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I'll never accept \Nthat he did it before us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.63,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you're hot stuff, you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! I'm the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. I really \Nexpected you to dodge.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you cranking one out\Nall by yourself in a training unit?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.69,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a wuss who just hitched a ride with a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You wanna go?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two said I piloted that thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The real thing ain't anything \Nlike the training units!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I get another chance, \NI'll show you I can pilot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge accepted!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Damn you! You're nothing but a loser!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lemme go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can pilot, too. I just need a chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.14,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nana.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A mock battle with me in a FRANXX?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on how you do,\Nwe're considering promoting you to parasite.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Grats!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick your partner.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you are {\i1}my{\i0} darling.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be his partner.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't belong to our squad.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you're only \Nmeasuring Hiro's aptitude,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it should work with me as his partner, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.26,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why does it have to be you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.02,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have Goro as a partner, \Nand you want to ride with Hiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go running your mouths now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.98,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two, HQ hasn't authorized \Nthe use of Strelizia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hiro will have to take the test \Nwith someone from his squad.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo. That sucks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. My injuries haven't \Nhealed completely yet, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you have him this time. Go for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of my darling, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll handle it, right, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone want to volunteer \Nas their opponents?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.72,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.27,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who died and made you boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.85,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show 'em what I'm capable of.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Done deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle will be held tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us do it right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorome's still mad about your fight today.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I know Ichigo's your partner.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hiro, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She never takes no for an answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make this chance count.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.65,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, wuss! Let's settle the \Nscore once and for all!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.40,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Given who your partner is, I might \Njust beat you this time, Great Leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't about winning or losing, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miku's totally up for it, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't about winning.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.79,0:17:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must prove to everyone that \NHiro can pilot the FRANXX!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just focus on connecting, Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Begin the mock battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.39,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll be all right. I can draw \Nout Hiro's ability, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This feeling...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm entering Ichigo's mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all right. Keep going.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where things get real.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! I recognize this sensation!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's do this, Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.76,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They stopped?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Time out! Give us three minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't just call timeout!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd it stop?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to pilot back then!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.84,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It just stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it my fault?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.18,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she do differently?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. No need to rush.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You might remember something.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiss...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the kiss.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kiss"? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We stuck our mouths together,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.58,0:19:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything turned bright, like, "Wham!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you were up to \Nduring a klaxosaur attack?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.75,0:19:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it as soon as I got in.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand what she was doing,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but Zero Two said it was \Na very special thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing, so keep your eyes closed.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't move unless we do it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.28,0:19:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.86,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what it takes,\NI don't mind. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichigo, you're trembling...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, hasn't it been three minutes already?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.00,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't see why we gotta wait any more.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.43,0:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we're taking you out.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.10,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is too easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it again, Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this proves that I'm really the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.34,0:20:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind taking over as \Npilot for the Delphinium, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.01,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're hitting on another girl now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out already, dude!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The trust between partners has a \Ndirect influence on the handling.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Should it be thrown out of whack...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Move...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Status report, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.79,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm trying!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichigo, don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Piloting a FRANXX alone is dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the reckless stunts...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.86,0:21:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since both FRANXX have been rendered \Ninoperable, this mock battle is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gentle touch of her trembling lips
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}filled me with guilt.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The feeling that I'd gotten to fly back then
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}quickly slipped through my fingers
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.96,0:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and eventually shackled me \Nto the ground once again.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.59,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It felt like I was being bound up \Nin a thousand invisible threads.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.14,0:22:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.03,0:22:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You were awful.
